sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import { Button } from '../ButtonElement' import { ImagedContainer, ImagedWrapper, ImagedRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, BtnWrap, Subtitle, ImgWrap, Img, } from './ImagedSectionElements' const ImagedSection = ({ id, lightBg, lightText, imgStart, topLine, headLine, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headLine} {description} ) } export default ImagedSection
